<bibRefCitation id="16704B1D2474BD2DFE7AD8B2198AA40B" author="Trail, W." box="[474,693,1776,1802]" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Botany" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" pagination="323 - 333" part="5" refId="ref124658" refString="Trail, W. (1876) Descriptions of new species and varieties of palm collected in the valley of the Amazon in north Brazil, in 1874. Journal of Botany 5: 323 - 333." title="Descriptions of new species and varieties of palm collected in the valley of the Amazon in north Brazil" type="journal article" year="1876">Trail (1876: 325)</bibRefCitation>
